&lt;p&gt;The initial part contains an anti-debugging check, specifically checking for
&lt;a href=&quot;https:&#x2F;&#x2F;x64.syscall.sh&#x2F;&quot;&gt;&lt;code&gt;ptrace&lt;&#x2F;code&gt;&lt;&#x2F;a&gt;:&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
&lt;pre data-lang=&quot;as&quot; class=&quot;language-as z-code&quot;&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;language-as&quot; data-lang=&quot;as&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;z-source z-actionscript z-2&quot;&gt;MOV EAX,&lt;span class=&quot;z-constant z-numeric z-actionscript z-2&quot;&gt;00000065&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;
