&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;&#x2F;code&gt;&lt;&#x2F;pre&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Using &lt;a href=&quot;https:&#x2F;&#x2F;github.com&#x2F;pwndbg&#x2F;pwndbg&quot;&gt;&lt;code&gt;pwndbg&#x2F;pwndbg&lt;&#x2F;code&gt;&lt;&#x2F;a&gt;, it’s a little more clear:&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
&lt;pre data-lang=&quot;as&quot; class=&quot;language-as z-code&quot;&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;language-as&quot; data-lang=&quot;as&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;z-source z-actionscript z-2&quot;&gt; ► &lt;span class=&quot;z-constant z-numeric z-actionscript z-2&quot;&gt;0x7ffff7fbf000&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;    mov    edi, &lt;span class=&quot;z-constant z-numeric z-actionscript z-2&quot;&gt;1&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;             EDI &lt;span class=&quot;z-keyword z-operator z-symbolic z-actionscript z-2&quot;&gt;=&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&amp;gt; &lt;span class=&quot;z-constant z-numeric z-actionscript z-2&quot;&gt;1&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;
