&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;z-source z-actionscript z-2&quot;&gt;   &lt;span class=&quot;z-constant z-numeric z-actionscript z-2&quot;&gt;0x7ffff7fbf013&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;    syscall  &amp;lt;SYS_ptrace&amp;gt;
&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;z-source z-actionscript z-2&quot;&gt;   &lt;span class=&quot;z-constant z-numeric z-actionscript z-2&quot;&gt;0x7ffff7fbf015&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;    cmp    rax, &lt;span class=&quot;z-constant z-numeric z-actionscript z-2&quot;&gt;0&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;
&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;&#x2F;code&gt;&lt;&#x2F;pre&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Setting &lt;code&gt;set $rax=0&lt;&#x2F;code&gt; right before that check is made to bypass it. The program
