&lt;a href=&quot;https:&#x2F;&#x2F;www.ons.gov.uk&#x2F;peoplepopulationandcommunity&#x2F;populationandmigration&#x2F;populationestimates&#x2F;bulletins&#x2F;annualmidyearpopulationestimates&#x2F;mid2022&quot;&gt;ONS&lt;&#x2F;a&gt;,
