&lt;p&gt;Dumping &lt;em&gt;all&lt;&#x2F;em&gt; the HTTP objects reveals a series of HTTP forms, the first of
which is:&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
&lt;pre data-lang=&quot;http&quot; class=&quot;language-http z-code&quot;&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;language-http&quot; data-lang=&quot;http&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;z-text z-plain&quot;&gt;result=rbqA0td2aIZzzE4Q5LYitDDQcpMz%2FgSbMWbTceiStH3ZK8VvGQxF%2BOc7%2Fp2PSgDw
