&lt;p&gt;There’s probably an easy way to mount each individually but instead, extracting
just the one of interest:&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
&lt;pre data-lang=&quot;sh&quot; class=&quot;language-sh z-code&quot;&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;language-sh&quot; data-lang=&quot;sh&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;z-source z-shell z-bash&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;z-meta z-function-call z-shell&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;z-variable z-function z-shell&quot;&gt;❯&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;z-meta z-function-call z-arguments z-shell&quot;&gt; dd if=obnoxious.img skip=2098176 of=obnoxious.img2 bs=1&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;
