&lt;p&gt;The 7th entry in that output is significant: &lt;code&gt;25&lt;&#x2F;code&gt;, &lt;code&gt;2e&lt;&#x2F;code&gt; and &lt;code&gt;78&lt;&#x2F;code&gt; are the hex
