the &lt;a href=&quot;https:&#x2F;&#x2F;blog.psypherpunk.io&#x2F;blog&#x2F;bsides-london-2023&#x2F;.&#x2F;2022-08-16-dialed-up-ctf.md&quot;&gt;&lt;em&gt;Dialed Up CTF&lt;&#x2F;em&gt;&lt;&#x2F;a&gt; here. And, as per that CTF,
&lt;a href=&quot;https:&#x2F;&#x2F;github.com&#x2F;ribt&#x2F;dtmf-decoder&quot;&gt;&lt;code&gt;ribt&#x2F;dtmf-decoder&lt;&#x2F;code&gt;&lt;&#x2F;a&gt; is
useful here:&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
