&lt;a href=&quot;https:&#x2F;&#x2F;www.dcode.fr&#x2F;multitap-abc-cipher&quot;&gt;here&lt;&#x2F;a&gt; suggest that this is &lt;code&gt;RMS&lt;&#x2F;code&gt; but
more likely:&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
&lt;pre data-lang=&quot;txt&quot; class=&quot;language-txt z-code&quot;&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;language-txt&quot; data-lang=&quot;txt&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;z-text z-plain&quot;&gt;SMS
