&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;z-text z-plain&quot;&gt;we&amp;#39;ve received the following data:
&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;z-text z-plain&quot;&gt;`111 100 100 000 001101 01 10 100 001101 0 0001 0 10 000`
