binary.&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The binary uses a key to XOR a base64-encoded ciphertext to the flag (both of
which are visible in a straight &lt;code&gt;strings&lt;&#x2F;code&gt; call):&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;the key is &lt;code&gt;bsides&lt;&#x2F;code&gt;.&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;the base64-encoded ciphertext is &lt;code&gt;GS0nLDoqUl8sLScsGA==&lt;&#x2F;code&gt;.&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
