&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;z-text z-plain&quot;&gt;Through the looking glass we go!  This sure looks a lot like the original, but
&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;z-text z-plain&quot;&gt;not... quite?
