&lt;p&gt;Those &lt;code&gt;90&lt;&#x2F;code&gt;&#x2F;&lt;code&gt;80&lt;&#x2F;code&gt; pairs correspond to key-on&#x2F;key-off commands in MIDI with the
last &lt;code&gt;40&lt;&#x2F;code&gt; indicating “velocity”. The middle hex digit is the actual note.&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
