wannabe. Perfect.&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The site itself seems to have little in the way of user input to exploit. Using
&lt;code&gt;ffuf&lt;&#x2F;code&gt; to scan for subdomain discovery turns up &lt;code&gt;dev.stocker.htb&lt;&#x2F;code&gt;:&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
