&lt;p&gt;The form itself doesn’t appear to be vulnerable to SQLi. The data is sent as
a standard HTML form:&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
&lt;pre data-lang=&quot;txt&quot; class=&quot;language-txt z-code&quot;&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;language-txt&quot; data-lang=&quot;txt&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;z-text z-plain&quot;&gt;username=admin&amp;amp;password=admin
