          <title>️🏴 Dialed Up CTF</title>
          <pubDate>Tue, 16 Aug 2022 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
          <author>PsypherPunk</author>
          <link>https://blog.psypherpunk.io/blog/dialed-up-ctf/</link>
